Thank you to the talented @benflyingretro for putting this together. I’ve been a fan of his page for a while. Song ‘Rising Up’ by Olivier Deriviere @oderiviere . Footage from @brettnovak @inlemediaco @apple @berrics @smileisaband @powellperalta 
#skateboard #skateboardingisfun #skateboarding

node.text:
“Virtuoso” (LINK IN BIO) now playing @berrics is a visual collaboration with @a_happy_medium_  The intention being to create something that would evoke the experience of viewing an interpretive dance performance. Accompanied by a hauntingly beautiful musical score performed by @radicalfaceofficial , this is a must watch for all of you artsy types 🤌

Directed and photographed by @hunteroshea
Shot on @reddigitalcinema & @kodak_shootfilm

#ahappymedium #ahappymediumskateboarding
#berrics #powellperalta @powellperalta #burntwhiskeybeardco @burntwhiskeybeardco #skateboardingisfun #esskateboarding
